  "monster": {
    "title": "Luedatz.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Luedatz has a slender green body with sparrow-like wings and huge, compound eyes.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 148     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: ++       </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: ++++     </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: +++       </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: +..     </lightgrey><lightgrey>   rC: ∞        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: +        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 170% (normally travels faster than you)\n\nYou have about 73% to hit with the earth staff of Heof.\nIt has about 24% to hit you.\n\nAttack  Max Damage    \nBite    61 (base 41)  \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to steam, acid and corrosion and miasma.\nIt is vulnerable to silver and hated by Zin.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can fly.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.\n\nIt is currently targeting the sin beast.\n\nThis monster has been temporarily summoned to this location. If angered it will immediately vanish, yielding no experience or items; it is incapable of using stairs.",
    "quote": "",
    "status": "<white>Fast:<lightgrey>\n   This creature moves and acts 50% faster.\n\n<white>Strong:<lightgrey>\n   This creature's melee attacks deal 50% more damage.\n\n<white>Unusually resistant:<lightgrey>\n   This creature's resistance to fire, cold, poison, electricity, and corrosion\n   are all increased by one level.\n\n<white>Sheltered from injuries:<lightgrey>\n   Half of the damage suffered by this creature is redirected to the ally\n   protecting it instead.\n\n<white>Lightly drained:<lightgrey>\n   This creature has been lightly drained, somewhat lowering the accuracy of\n   their melee attacks, the power of their spells and special attack properties,\n   and making them slightly more vulnerable to many status effects.\n\n",
    "spellset": [
      {
        "label": "\nIt possesses the following magical abilities, which are affected by antimagic (but not silence):",
